add repositories two ways:

a) add-apt-repository command 

	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:libreoffice/ppa

	OR

	add-apt-repository 'deb http://archive.getdeb.net/ubuntu wily-getdeb games'

b) create file manually 

	create a file in /etc/apt/sources.list.d directory, the file name must end with .list extension

	For example:

		1) vim /etc/apt/sources.list.d/games.list
		
		Add the repository paths as below.
	
		2) deb http://archive.getdeb.net/ubuntu wily-getdeb games
	
	

